```plantuml
@startuml ballerina-platform_asyncapi-tools

[AsyncAPI CLI] as CLI
[AsyncAPI/OpenAPI Parser] as Parser
[Code Generator] as Generator
[Ballerina Exporter] as Exporter
[WebSocket Handler] as WSHandler
[Authentication Manager] as AuthManager
[Error Handler] as ErrorHandler
[Data Type Mapper] as TypeMapper
[Template Engine] as TemplateEngine

database "API Definitions" as APIDefs
database "Ballerina Code" as BallerinaCode

CLI --> Parser : Parses input
CLI --> Generator : Triggers generation
CLI --> Exporter : Triggers export

Parser --> APIDefs : Reads
Parser --> Generator : Provides parsed data

Generator --> TemplateEngine : Uses
Generator --> TypeMapper : Uses
Generator --> AuthManager : Configures auth
Generator --> WSHandler : Configures WebSocket
Generator --> BallerinaCode : Generates

Exporter --> BallerinaCode : Reads
Exporter --> APIDefs : Generates

WSHandler --> ErrorHandler : Uses

@enduml
```